  "title": "Student Care Educator",
  "description": "<ul><li>Engage with children through play, interaction, and daily classroom routines.</li><li>Plan and conduct fun and age-appropriate activities to support children’s learning and development.</li><li>Teach positive values and support children’s social, emotional, and moral growth.</li><li>Set up a safe and suitable learning environment according to KCare safety and health guidelines.</li><li>Build good relationships with parents and update them on their children’s progress and development.</li><li>Organise and lead both indoor and outdoor activities to keep children engaged throughout the day.</li><li>Ensure the safety and well-being of all children and observe any health or developmental concerns.</li><li>Provide care, comfort, and emotional support to children when needed.</li><li>Maintain discipline and order in the classroom and playground.</li><li>Carry out any other tasks assigned by the supervisor..</li></ul><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.<br /></p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd <br />EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
